{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were given these special peak caps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One of the calamities that occurred was that we were all equipped with long trousers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, in Germany in those days, one didn't go into long trousers as a boy until the age of 18 or 19.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Here we were-- my brother was 8 and I was 12 or 13 by that time-- in long trousers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First of all, the material was such that it was terribly rough on our legs, the dainty little legs that the spoiled brats had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I always used to wear pajama trousers underneath the-- the long trousers, because my legs were totally stiff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I couldn't sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I couldn't bend my leg, I felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were allowed-- and we had a blazer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a badge on here that indicated Rowden Hall School, which was the name of the thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was all quite pleasant and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were allowed to go-- Margate was, of course, a seaside resort not too far away from London.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at weekends, people came from London and relaxed for a couple of days or perhaps for a day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In those days, working on Saturdays was still very, very common.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was the order of the-- the day, as it were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were allowed to walk around on the beach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The house was right by the seafront, in a very beautiful position.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were allowed to go into town and do whatever we wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But on Saturdays and Sundays, we were, as it were, confined to barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And on inquiries why that was so, we were being told, which was painful, that a lot of very hard-working people came down from London to relax.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
